criteria.textblock:
        RECRUITED IN JAIL

          1. Diagnosed HIV+;

          2. ages 18-25 and 364 days;

          3. non-cis woman;

          4. English language fluency;

          5. anticipated sentence of no more than 12 months;

          6. Residing in Southern California (Los Angeles, Kern, San Diego, Riverside, Ventura or
             San Bernardino Counties) or Cook County, IL upon release

        RECRUITED OUTSIDE OF JAIL

          1. Diagnosed HIV+;

          2. ages 16-25 and 364 days;

          3. non-cis woman;

          4. English language fluency;

          5. Incarceration history within the last 12 months of enrollment;

          6. Residing in Southern California (Los Angeles, Kern, San Diego, Riverside, Ventura or
             San Bernardino Counties) or Cook County, IL upon release

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1. Inability to give informed consent; 2. Parole hold or transfer to prison
